    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ In nomine Domini. Vicesimo anno principatus domni nostri <persName
                            ref="#people/4105" key="#Princeps">Gisulfi</persName> gloriosi princeps,
                        mense octobri, quintadecima indictione. Dum coram presentia domni <persName
                            ref="#people/4191" key="#Abbots #Monks">Leonis</persName> venerabilis
                            <rs key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/225" key="#Monasteries">Sancte et individue
                            Trinitatis</orgName> quod foris anc civitatem in loco <placeName
                            ref="#places/4755" key="#Villages/settlements #Monasteries"
                            >Metiliano</placeName> constructum est, essem ego <persName
                            ref="#people/4161" key="#Count #Judge">Sico</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs> et <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs>, et ibidem
                        adesset <persName key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus" ref="#people/4194"
                            >Vivo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">castaldeus</rs> filius quondam Petri et
                        ydonei homines interessent. </ab>
                    <ab>Ipse domnus abbas ostendens unum preceptum utili anulo consignatum scriptum
                        per <persName ref="#people/4149" key="#Writer #Clergy/religious_persons"
                            >Aceprandum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Clergy/religious_persons">lebitam</rs> et <rs key="#Writer"
                            >scribam</rs> sacri palatii presente anno et indictione et preterito
                        mense septembri; qualiter ipse domnus <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>
                        concesserat in ipso monasterio et ipsi Vivo <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >terram</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Houses #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >casam</rs> fabritam que fuerat <name
                            ref="Petrus clericus f. qd. Alfani">Petri</name> clerici filii quondam
                        Alfani intra hanc <placeName ref="#places/84"
                            key="#Cities #Houses #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >civitatem</placeName> prope portam que dicitur de la Palma, et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >terram</rs> in quam valneum construendum inceptum habebant et aque que
                        ibi a super surgunt et aliud sicut ipsum preceptum continet. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
